<!DOCTYPE HTML>

<html>

<head>
	<title>Login Task App</title>
	<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Poppins:600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
	<script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/a81368914c.js"></script>
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
	<style>
		body {
			margin: 0;
			font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', 'Oxygen', 'Ubuntu', 'Cantarell', 'Fira Sans', 'Droid Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
			font-weight: 300;
			-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
			-moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
			line-height: 1.6;
		}

		.background {
			padding-bottom: 20px;
			width: 80%;
			margin: 0 auto;
		}

		.wave {
			height: 200px;
			width: 100vw;
			position: absolute;
			top: 0;
			left: 0;
			z-index: -1;
		}

		h1 {
			text-align: center;
		}

		h2 {
			margin-top: 50px;
		}
		.label{
			text-transform: capitalize;
		}
		.container :nth-child(1) {
			font-weight: 600;
		}

		.container {
			margin: 25px 0;
			padding: 5px 0;
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 70%30%;
			justify-content: space-between !important;
			border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(200, 200, 200, 0.5);
		}

		.title {
			font-weight: 600;
			flex: 1 1;
		}

		.footer {
			margin: 25px 0;
		}

		.main-title {
			background-color: #9fd7ff;
			color: #fff;
			height: 150px;
			text-transform: capitalize;
		}

		.main-title h1 {
			margin: 0;
			padding: 50px 0;
		}
	</style>
</head>

<body>
	<div>
		<!-- <div class="main-title">
            <h1>Studio radiologico Lecca Deiana</h1>
        </div> -->
		<div class="background">
			<h1>Annullamento cancellazione</h1>
			<div class="confirm-container">
				<p>Gentile {{name}}, le confermiamo l'annullamento della sua prenotazione.<br> Di seguito un riepilogo della prenotazione cancellata
				</p>
				<h2>Riepilogo prenotazione</h2>
				<div class="container">
					<label class="title">Nome</label>
					<label>{{name}}</label>
				</div>
				<div class="container">
					<label class="title">Esame</label>
					<label>{{exam}}</label>
				</div>
				<div class="container">
					<label class="title">Data</label>
					<label>{{date}}</label>
				</div>
				<div class="container">
					<label class="title">Orario</label>
					<label>{{time}}</label>
				</div>
				<p>Cordiali saluti,<br> Studio Radiologico Dott Fabrizio Lecca, Dott Elisabetta Deiana.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>

</html>